data.description: Welcome to your future oasis! This fantastic property boasts a sprawling corner lot and a private courtyard-style patio that you can access from both the family room and the primary bedroom ? talk about practical living! The kitchen is the heart of the home, opening up to the dining and living areas for seamless entertaining. Picture this: a step-down family room, perfect for those cozy gatherings, a spacious laundry room for added convenience, and not one, but two gas fireplaces in both the family room and bedroom for ultimate warmth and charm. The primary bedroom? Oh, it's not just a bedroom ? it comes with an extra room, ideal for creating your dream office, nursery, gym, or whatever your heart desires. Get ready to turn this house into your vibrant and happy home!
